{"id":4117,"content":"<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 77.6pt; mso-char-indent-count: 8.34\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.5pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">这是我国杰出的画家和美术教育家徐悲鸿（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1895</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">—</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1953</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">年），</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1931</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">年创作的中国画《九方皋》。纸本，彩墨，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">35</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">0</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">×<SPAN lang=EN-US>138</SPAN>厘米，徐悲鸿纪念馆藏。这里是根据<B>他的画册<SUP>【<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>】</SUP></B>制作的。<BR><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" align=center><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\"><o:p><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"><IMG height=304 alt=\"\" src=\"/upFiles/czhang20028tubian/2009011219200689394.jpg\" width=640 border=0>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<FONT face=黑体>&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><FONT face=黑体>《九方皋》</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=黑体>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</FONT> </SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">一．取材</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18.35pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.98\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">这幅画取材于</SPAN><FONT color=#6e0707><SPAN class=tpccontent1><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\">《列子</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN class=tpccontent1><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana\">·</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN class=tpccontent1><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\">说符》<SUP>【</SUP></SPAN></B></SPAN><SPAN class=tpccontent1><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SUP><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana\">2</SPAN></SUP></B></SPAN><SPAN class=tpccontent1><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SUP><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\">】</SPAN></SUP></B></SPAN><SPAN class=tpccontent1><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\">中的故事。那里说的是：</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　秦穆公对伯乐说：“您的年岁高了！您的子孙中有可以派去寻求天下好马的人吗？”伯乐答道：“我的儿子们都是才能一般的人，能够教会他们识别一般的好马，无法教他们识别天下特出的千里马。我有一个曾在一起扛过东西打过柴草的朋友，叫九方皋，这个人对于马的识别本领不在我之下，可以叫他来见您。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　秦穆公召见了九方皋，派他外出找马，三个月后返回报告说：“已经得到它了，在沙丘。”穆公问：“什么马？”答道：“是一匹黄色母马。”派人前去取得它，却是一匹黑色公马。穆公不高兴，召唤伯乐对他说：“糟糕，你所派遣的找马人！毛色、雌雄尚且不能知道，又能知道什么好马？”伯乐长长地叹息道：“竟然到了这种地步吗？九方皋相马的事，正是所以比我强千万倍还不止啊！像九方皋的观察，是天地间的奥妙：得其精而忘其粗，在其内而忘其外，见其所见，不见其所不见。像他这种善于识别千里马的人，实在是比千里马更宝贵啊！”马牵来了，果然是天下特出的好马啊。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">这是一个颇为复杂的故事，试看画家如何表现？</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><o:p><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">二．赏析</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.5pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">画面截取九方皋面对马群观察过程的<B>一个瞬间<SUP>【</SUP></B></SPAN><B><SUP><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">3</FONT></SPAN></SUP></B><B><SUP><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，</SPAN></SUP></B><B><SUP><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">4</FONT></SPAN></SUP></B><B><SUP><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">】</SPAN></SUP></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">栩栩如生地塑造了一位朴实的劳动者——九方皋的形象。画家选取九方皋相马的情态为表现的主题。他正在聚精会神地察看面前的那些马。但从视角来看，他并不着眼于马的皮毛蹄腿。他仿佛正在体察这匹黑马的精神气质。而这正是九方皋之所以为相马名家的所在。而那匹黑色的公马，仿佛突然见到了知音，它发出快乐的嘶鸣，扬起钢铁般的蹄子跃跃欲试。画中的其他人物都做为陪衬的配角，每人都个性鲜明，神态各异，分别从不同的角度的侧面，烘托出九方皋的智慧和胸有成竹的神态。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18.35pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.98\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">徐悲鸿一生致力于中国画革新的伟大实践。在国外掌握了西洋画解剖知识和造型手段的徐悲鸿，试图在中国画中融入这些因素。虽然他仍以线条为主，辅以较单纯的色彩塑造人物，但对人体和肌肉的表现已相当重视。这从牵马人的前胸、四肢都可以明显地看出。当他描绘那匹黑马时，已将黑色的渲染和结构的体面关系糅合在一起，丰富了中国画的语言，也呈现出鲜明的徐悲鸿风格。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.5pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">西洋画重写实，中国画重写意。所谓写意，是指中国画的一种传统画法。着笔不求工细，而使用简练的线条和墨色（有时也用色彩），注重所描绘人或物的神态的表现和抒发作者的情趣（跟工笔画<B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\">相区别）<SUP>【</SUP></B></SPAN><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SUP><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">5</FONT></SPAN></SUP></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SUP><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，</SPAN></SUP></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SUP><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">6</FONT></SPAN></SUP></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SUP><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">】</SPAN></SUP></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">。徐悲鸿擅长画马，独具特色。他笔下的马，都是有灵性、通人性的。看是画马，实为表现人的情感。用这种视角，能从悲鸿的画中，“读”出许多深层的内涵。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.5pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">徐悲鸿画马作品很多。他笔下的马都是奔放不羁的野马，从来不带缰辔。例如这幅</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1939</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年创作的《群奔》。<SPAN style=\"COLOR: black\">骏马之间的组合关系、它们爽朗明快的精神面貌、以及它们相互之间神情上的顾盼关系，都表现得极为精妙。这里体现出了徐悲鸿艺术精神上的<B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\">浪漫主义情怀<SUP>【</SUP></B></SPAN></SPAN><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SUP><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">7</FONT></SPAN></SUP></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SUP><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">】</SPAN></SUP></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">。给人以精神独立、思想自由、情感豪迈、勇往直前的启迪。这些，与带</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">缰辔的马相比，别有一番情趣。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" align=center><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><o:p><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;<IMG style=\"WIDTH: 544px; HEIGHT: 250px\" height=32 alt=\"\" src=\"/upFiles/czhang20028tubian/2009011219200697680.jpg\" width=28 border=0></FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT face=黑体>《群奔》</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><o:p><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.5pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">但在《九方皋》画面上那匹黑色雄马，却例外地戴上了缰辔。有人问悲鸿：“这是为什么呢？”悲鸿笑着答道：“马和人一样，愿为知己者用，不愿为昏庸者制。”由此可见徐悲鸿的思想和用心。他为什么创作这幅画？</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: #cc0033; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 141.3pt; mso-char-indent-count: 15.24\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">三．创作动机</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">徐悲鸿生在画师之家，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">6</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">岁随父读书，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">9</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">岁在父亲督导下学画，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">13</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">岁随父亲辗转于乡里卖画，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">17</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">岁独自到上海卖画谋生。因父亲病重回到家乡，在三处学校担任国画教师，以负担全家的生活。不久，父亲及悲鸿新婚的妻子相继去世，其人生旅程益加艰难。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">20</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">岁二度赴沪谋生，但却处处碰壁。后来的妻子蒋碧薇，受高官引诱与他离婚，并多次对他进行敲诈勒索。直到与廖静文结合以后，生活在有<B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\">了转机<SUP>【</SUP></B></SPAN><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SUP><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">4</SPAN></SUP></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SUP><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">】</SPAN></SUP></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">。悲鸿大师一生坎坷，只活了</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">58</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">岁。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18.35pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.98\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">徐悲鸿有感于自己的身世遭际，有感于许多有才学的人不为世人所识，而以九方皋相马的故事为题材创作了此画。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.5pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">悲鸿有感于这个动人的故事，正是由于他亲眼看到了在当时的政府统治下，大量人才被压抑、被埋没的现状；也是他亲身感受到要提携、培养一个有才华的人是何等的艰难；同时，他永远也忘不了自己为生活所迫几乎投江自尽的悲惨经历……所有这一切，都激发着悲鸿的创作欲望。他借《九方皋》倾吐内心的抑郁，抒发渴望发掘人<B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\">才的美好意愿<SUP>【</SUP></B></SPAN><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SUP><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">3</FONT></SPAN></SUP></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SUP><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">】</SPAN></SUP></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.5pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">所以九方皋的故事和徐悲鸿的那幅画，表面上看是涉及相马。实际上讲的是发掘、培养人才，并使之充分发挥作用艰难。这是一个制度问题。韩愈的文章说得更清楚。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.5pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><o:p><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 119.3pt; mso-char-indent-count: 12.87\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">四．伯乐相马的启示</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.5pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">韩愈的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">《马说》的原文是：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.5pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">世有伯乐，然后有千里马。千里马常有，而伯乐不常有。故虽有名马，只辱于奴隶人之手，骈死于槽枥之间，不以千里称也。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">　　马之千里者，一食或尽粟一石。食马者，不知其能千里而食也。是马也，虽有千里之能，食不饱，力不足，才美不见外，且欲与常马等不可得，安求其能千里也</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\">!<BR></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">策之不以其道，食之不能尽其材，鸣之而不能通其意，执策而临之曰：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\">“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">天下无马。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\">”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">呜呼！其真无马邪？其真不知马也</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\">!</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">白话译文是：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18.35pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.98\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">世上有了伯乐，然后才会有千里马被发现。可是千里马虽然世代常有，而伯乐却不常有，因此虽然有不少好马，却只能在马夫手中受糟塌，最后接连不断地死在马厩之中，而不能以千里马著名。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\"> <BR></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">　　那些千里马，一顿往往要吃尽一石小米。可是喂马的人，不知道它能日行千里，只是象对凡马一般地饲养它。于是，那些好马，虽然有日行千里的本领，可是吃不饱，力气不足，它们的骨力特长因此不能表现出来，这样，即使想与凡马一般也不可能，哪里还能叫它日行千里呢？</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\"> <BR></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">　　（现在那些养马的人，自己不知道手中有千里马），因此驾驭时不能顺其本性；喂养时又不能给料充足，使它充分发挥才能；马虽然哀鸣，人却一点不懂得它的意思。还拿着马鞭，煞有介事地对它说：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\">“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">天下没有千里马！</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\">”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">唉！这难道是真的没有千里马呢，还是确实不识千里马呢。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">这篇文章提出了</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\"> <SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">个问题：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\">1. </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">好马很多，但能识马的人少，它们难于被发现。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\">2. </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">好马不被认识，人们还象对一般马那样，喂养时不能给料充足，驾驭时不能顺其本性，更不能与它进行交流。因而不能使好马发挥应有的作用。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\">3. </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">关键不在没好马，而在缺少伯乐那样的人，去识别与正确对待他们。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">这就是伯乐制的缺陷与困境。要解决，只能跳出“伯乐制”，采用</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\"> </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">“赛场制”。其含义如下：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>1. </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">马的素质，是一般、是好马、还是千里马，不靠相马人识别，而靠所有的马在竞赛场（包括野马自由参加的）上的竞赛决定。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\">2. </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">选马的主顾们，在比赛现场，根绝自己的意愿，直接（不借助伯乐）、自由选择所要的对象。与马双方订立契约。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\">3. </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">主顾对马要精心饲养、顺其本性驾驭，充分它的作用。否则这种和人和马的关系随时可以改变。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">采用这种“赛场制”的话，伯乐制的问题与困境，即可解决。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">半个多世纪以来，“伯乐相马”之说，在国内及执政党内，常被提起，流传相当广泛。尤其是“世有伯乐，然后有千里马。千里马常有，而伯乐不常有。”道出问题症结的这句话，已成为脍炙人口的名句。不管是</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">韩愈</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">《马说》的原意，还是应用者的用意，都是用寓言方式谈论人才选拔、培养、对待的问题。以下，让我们从寓言返回人间社会。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 107.55pt; mso-char-indent-count: 11.6\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">五．人事制度的改革</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">中国两千多年来的经济体制，是以家庭为生产单位的自给自足的自然经济，加上一些官办的企业，构成<B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\">统制经济</B></SPAN><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SUP><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">[9]</FONT></SPAN></SUP></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">。</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">其特征是商品交换不发达，也是一种简单的计划经济。新中国成立以后照搬苏联模式建立起来了计划经济。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1978</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年起开始由计划经济向市场经济的转轨。经济基础的变化，逐渐引起上层建筑内，人事制度的变革。这里的“人事制度”的含义，包括一般工作人员的安排、各级政府官员的确定两个方面。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 39.35pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; tab-stops: list 39.35pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo3\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Times New Roman\"><SPAN style=\"mso-list: Ignore\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1.<SPAN style=\"FONT: 7pt Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">一般工作人员的安排</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18.35pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.98\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">计划经济体制下的人事制度，简单说就是统一分配。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">50</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年前我们这一代人大学毕业时，流行的口号是：“站出来让祖国挑选”、“服从组织分配”、“到祖国最需要的地方去”、“一生交给党安排”等。这种情况下，个人的志趣、专长的发挥，自然有很大的局限。专业不对口的情况，时有发生。想要更换单位，很不容易。即使有这样的想法，也会被认为是在“闹情绪”，从而进行教育，劝你“安心工作”。在一个单位一干就是几十年直至退休，是常见的事。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18.35pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.98\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">现在，情况有了很大的变化。双向选择、竞争上岗的聘任制，取代了过去的“分配制”。人才合理流动的渠道，也很畅通。每个青年发展，在这种赛场之下，有了更优越的环境。令人羡慕而不嫉妒。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 39.35pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; tab-stops: list 39.35pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo3\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Times New Roman\"><SPAN style=\"mso-list: Ignore\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2.<SPAN style=\"FONT: 7pt Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">各级政府官员的确定</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18.35pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.98\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">自从秦王朝建立郡县制以来，各级政府的行政长官，都由上级决定、派出。从上到下，层层节制，形成了一种官本位的、金字塔形的权力结构。人们的升迁与否，是由上级官员是否赏识决定的。这是一种典型的“伯乐制”。这种情况，即使在改革开放</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">30</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年来，也没有多大变化。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18.35pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.98\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">与此形成对照的宪政民主制度下，各级政府的行政长官，都有自下而上的民主选举确定。人们的升迁与否，是由选民根据他们的素质与行为，所投的票数决定的。可称之为“赛场制”。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-","title":"巨幅中国画《九方皋》观赏有感","time":1231787217999}